data.description: CURRENTLY UNDER CONTRACT, SELLER WILL CONSIDER BACKUP OFFERS.  PRICE REDUCED!!!   Come see this one!  Introducing 5610 Merritt Brown Road, the lowest priced home in Cherokee Heights, one of Bay County's most popular neighborhoods. This 3 bedroom (4th bedroom is in a separate building), 2 bath home was renovated in 2019 with new roof and interior renovation too.  The interior is an open floor plan with one large room for the eat in kitchen and living room. As a bonus there is a dining room that is currently being used as a den. The master suite is separated frm the rest of home and boasts a large walk in closet, double vanities, large tub and separate shower.  Bedrooms 2 and 3 are also large and share a full bath. Bedroom #4 is located in a separate building behind the home. There is also a storage room PLUS attic storage in the separate building as well as attic storage in the home. This bonus room is perfect for in laws, live ins, or just a good place for guests.  The exterior of the home is easy to maintain vinyl and the back yard is fully fenced in.  The HVAC system has also been replaced, this one is move in and live with no worries!  There is a large paver patio AND a Florida room for more space.  Cherokee Heights is popular due to proximity to Schools, shopping, employment and super close to Tyndall AFB.  NO HOA, lower taxes and great neighbors make this neighborhood great.  Call today to see this one.  Square footage is an approximation, please measure if important.
